Scope of this license

This MIT license covers ONLY the build tooling in this repository — the code
and configuration that fetches, assembles, and compiles content, including:

    anthropic_resources.py   fetch_docs.py   build_book.py
    Makefile   metadata.yaml   manifest.txt   frontmatter/   test_*.py

It does NOT cover, and confers no rights to, the third-party material this
tooling downloads, compiles, or produces. That material — Anthropic's Claude
documentation, cookbooks, courses, engineering essays, and the cloned official
repositories — remains under its original copyright and licenses (© Anthropic
and the respective repository licenses). The compiled ebooks (EPUB / AZW3) and
the fetched `docs/` and `anthropic-collection/` content are NOT licensed for
redistribution and are intentionally excluded from this repository via
`.gitignore`.

In short: the tool is MIT-licensed and free to use; the content it assembles
is not yours (or this project's) to relicense or redistribute. Compile it for
your own offline study. The canonical, always-current sources live at
docs.claude.com, code.claude.com, and github.com/anthropics.
